Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:07.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have the power to protect \Nmy friends, that's all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.54,0:00:12.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could trade for that power, \NI wouldn't care how weak I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess... that's contradictory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:20.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are an interesting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:23.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could fight you fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:25.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:28.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean that time is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.19,0:02:04.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:08.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Each side presses the other as the \Nbattle on Tenroujima continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:12.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bluenote appeared before Natsu's group.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:17.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not one of the 7 Kin of Purgatory, \Nbut the second-in-command!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:21.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The odds were stacked higher \Nand higher against Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.86,0:02:27.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But then Fried, Bickslow, and \NGildarts came running back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:30.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail started to gain some momentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:35.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But then something happened on Tenroujima \Nthat no one could have even imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:39.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The land where Fairy Tail's \Nfounding master rests...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:43.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What future could Mavis's will \Nilluminate for Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:56.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:58.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:02.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Power... I can't gather any strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All the energy from my body \Nis being drained suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:08.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:13.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana? Cana!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:15.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:21.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... so weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:23.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep... my eyes open...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:25.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:28.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I secretly ate some \Nfish just a little while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:33.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beat... I think I'm done...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:34.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:36.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could... this be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our magic power?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that shaking before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:00.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuma, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My strength... It's being drained.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:08.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like he felled the Tenrou Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:14.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's stealing the magic power from all \Nthe people with the mark of Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:16.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:19.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:22.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect this was an \Norder from Master Hades.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.25,0:04:25.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I helping her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:32.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza vs. Azuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:38.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:43.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have control over the island's magic \Npower, but have left yours alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:45.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Titania.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:48.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All around the island, your \Ncomrades are facing certain death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:53.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You shall show me just how great this \N"power to protect your friends" is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:57.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You called yourself Azuma, one \Nof the 7 Kings of Purgatory, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:59.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Master Hades's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:06.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He told us to get rid of every Fairy \NTail wizard, without exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:07.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that you purposefully \Nleft me free to act?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:11.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you why.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:15.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to fight you seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:16.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:21.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that is the truth you speak,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:25.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then the moment I defeat you, you \Nwill return everyone's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:30.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, this is not how I \Nwould prefer to do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:36.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's only if you win, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:40.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends' lives lie in the balance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:41.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I assure you, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:43.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip! Heaven's Wheel Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:47.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:50.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blumenblatt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:05:59.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Folium Sica!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:04.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ramus Sica!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:17.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the Titania I was expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:20.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to come at me with all you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:34.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:37.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the Soaring Armor I've heard about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:38.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:49.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Adamantine Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:58.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one that defended against a \Ndirect hit from the Magic Focusing Cannon, Jupiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:00.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:06.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But can it defend against this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:33.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Thunder Empress Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:37.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see now. Your magic power does \Njustice to your name, Titania.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:42.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick Requipping, and flawless swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:50.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed. This is quite enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:54.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Great Tree Ark magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:55.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:59.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! It seems you are not just all talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:02.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't obessed about \Npeople's strength for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:04.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you fight me at full strength now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:08.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that won't be enough to stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:56.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her magic power's increasing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:05.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't break through even with the \Nmagic power of the Purgatory Armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:10.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have overestimated \Nyour armor's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:12.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were completely unguarded from below!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:15.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tower Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:44.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This man... What incredible magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:47.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He is truly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:51.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fairy's Armor is still damaged...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't have any other armor \Nthat'll be a match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:56.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:09:59.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:03.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought that Seduction Armor last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:05.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, I might...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:10.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:12.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Lucy, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:13.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:17.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:23.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To overcome his magic power, I have to \Ncollect all of mine and focus it into an attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use any magic power for defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:40.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I won't use any defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:42.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will concentrate all of \Nmy magic into my sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:49.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A sword you can't even grip unless \Nyou discard all defense...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:53.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold, the Fairy Sword, Benizakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:02.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My defeat means defeat for the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be my last stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:07.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Titania!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:09.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:12.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:15.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will put everything into this one attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:23.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:33.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Release the magic power of "Tenrou" \Nthat sleeps in the great land!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:38.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move... Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The cries of the great land...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:44.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Terra Clamare!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:17.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Titania... defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:40.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:53.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tenrou Tree has been destroyed by Azuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:56.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, the divine \Nprotection that should be given
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:12:59.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to all who bear the mark of \NFairy Tail has disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:03.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, their magic power is being drained.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:07.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fried and Gildarts are no exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:12.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The fate of the guild lies now on \Nthe shoulders of one person, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:20.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can anyone move?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:26.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. I don't know why, but \Nmy magic power is draining out of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:29.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:33.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have something to do with the \Ntree on the center of the island falling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:39.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do? Cana's completely \Nlost consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:42.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we still make it to the camp somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:44.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Things aren't good over here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:47.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps's breathing has gotten weaker...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:54.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone else safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:08.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something, Siegrain-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:12.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! He's Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:15.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the real identity of the \Nformer council member, Siegrain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:17.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, old habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:21.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He destroyed our Magic Council!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:25.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a villain who made people \Nlose all confidence in us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:32.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... You think he's casting \Na spell or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in a cage made of magic sealing stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:38.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't use magic of any kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to test him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:42.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:52.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Jellal, but he can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:54.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come on, Nadal... Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:15:01.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been muttering to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:18.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, we haven't \Nbeen giving you much food lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:21.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You hungry or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:27.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Try saying, "Please \Ngive me food, Nadal-sama"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:30.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask nicely, and I'll allow you to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:31.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:35.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you don't, then no meals for a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:42.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Er...za...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:47.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:55.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose... Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:30.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:33.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were hit with a massive amount \Nof Tenroujima's magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:47.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I just hear Jellal's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:50.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:55.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be weak... He's no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be misled by emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:00.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Center your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:06.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will stand up, to protect everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:36.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Frightening...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:51.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I lack the footwork?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:56.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know whether I'll be able \Nto win with the magic power I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:18:02.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the difference in "weight" \Nhe and I carry is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:06.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as he says, right now, \Neveryone's lives are riding on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:09.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I must protect them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The guild... My friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:16.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For their sake, I {\i1}will{\i0} win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:39.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so formidable that my heart is racing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:45.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail's Titania, Erza Scarlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:49.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure not to forget your \Nname, as long as I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:51.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:55.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's name you "Erza Scarlet"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:19:00.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scarlet. The color of your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, I'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:04.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the color of your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:20.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:22.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:25.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have another taste of the \Nmagic power of Tenroujima!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:32.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Terra Clamare!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:12.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:20.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:28.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:33.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:35.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:45.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:54.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:03.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:08.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten one crucial thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:14.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not protecting everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:16.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:25.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is I... who is always... being protected!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:39.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenroujima's magic power that I should \Nhave under control is protecting Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:42.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust... Bonds...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:47.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her true strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:50.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not "One", but "Many"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:55.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What an amazing guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:21:58.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.45,0:23:58.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, have you seen Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.35,0:23:59.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.45,0:24:02.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, haven't \Nseen Juvia either. What're they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:04.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray and Juvia? Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.53,0:24:06.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't heard this in a while:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.11,0:24:08.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They llllllike each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.45,0:24:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, calm down a bit, it's not {\i1}that{\i0} exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:16.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Frozen Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.00,0:24:20.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, wasn't Juvia with Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.05,0:24:21.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.77,0:24:23.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to happen to Gray, exactly?
